===message:I wonder if part of the tension was not planned to help bring cohesion and patriotism into the nations.   It seems to me this would be a great way to get people to work together against a common enemy. Governments could use the tension to convince people that they needed to sacrifice personally for the cause of capitalism or communism, depending on what side you were on. 

